ce:section.ce:para:
In addition to black mass, many other materials are handled during battery recycling process, such as graphite, aluminium, copper, iron, and plastic, etc. In this report, we focus exclusively on black mass, graphite, and aluminium. The dust explosion characteristics include maximum explosion overpressure (
P max
), deflagration index (
K St
), minimum ignition energy, and minimum ignition temperature of dust layer and cloud. The data have been collected from various sources including (i) a report by Beck et al. (1997), (ii) Gestis-Dust-Ex database (2024), (iii) a book by Eckhoff (2003), and (iv) other publications.
